  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractHitAndRunSampler
    Samples points in a constrained continuous Markov random field, using the "hit-and-run" sampling scheme described in Broecheler and Getoor, "Computing marginal distributions over continuous Markov networks for statistical relational learning." NIPS 2010.
